<h2>
    percent Pipe in Agular
</h2>

<h2>
    Syntax : Number_Expression | percent : digitsInfo

    Note : digitsInfo is 'minIntegerDigits.minFractionDigits-maxFractionDigits'
</h2>

<p>
    Number withtout percent Pipe : {{0.259}}
</p>

<p>
    Number With percent Pipe : {{0.259 | percent : '1.0-0'}}
</p>

<p>
    Number With percent Pipe : {{0.259 | percent : '1.1-1'}}
</p>

<p>
    Number With percent Pipe : {{0.259 | percent : '1.2-2'}}
</p>

<p>
    Number With percent Pipe : {{0.259 | percent : '1.0-3' }}
</p>


